These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
Movie-Genre: spy, comedy, mystery, western
1. Movie-Genre:comedy is in an odd position##4
2. Movie-Genre:western is between Movie-Genre:spy and Movie-Genre:comedy##2
3. Movie-Genre:western is on the right of Movie-Genre:spy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | western | comedy | mystery |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
Job: manager, engineer, entrepreneur, designer
1. Job:manager is on the left of Job:designer##1
2. Job:engineer is in an odd position##4
3. Job:engineer is on the left or right of Job:manager##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Job   | engineer | manager | designer | entrepreneur |

 #################################
 
