.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
Birthday: january, april, february, october
1. Birthday:april == Birthday:april##1
2. Birthday:october is on the left or right of Birthday:february##3
3. Birthday:february is on the far left or far right##3
4. Birthday:january is in an even position##4
5. Birthday:october is on the left of Birthday:april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Birthday   | february | october | april | january |

 #################################
 
